text: Typhoon Rammasun (known in the Philippines as Typhoon Glenda) was a 2014 Pacific Ocean typhoon. It affected Guam. It was expected to come to the Philippines, Taiwan, eastern China and Vietnam. As of July 18, the storm's winds were . Storm notices and warnings were activated from the Philippines to Vietnam and China. The Philippine threat from this typhoon was especially strong. ==Impact== As of July 18, the typhoon had killed 38 people in the Philippines. ==References== Category:Pacific typhoons Category:2014 in weather Category:History of Guam Category:Retired tropical cyclone names
title: Typhoon Rammasun
